headline: 2 Industrials Stocks to Stash and 1 to Sell
summary: Whether you see them or not, industrials businesses play a crucial part in our daily activities. Still, their generally high capital requirements expose them to the ups and downs of economic cycles, and the industry’s six-month return of 13% has fallen short of the S&P 500’s 16.8% rise.
